Quote:  And while I was being thoughtful, my eyes, glancing down into the street from the window, noted that a quite ordinary-looking middle-aged man, by exercising the most surprising cunning as he paused at an open alleyway, and greatly assisted by a newspaper which he appeared to be reading, was contriving to jerry-riddle quite unnoticed by passers-by and particularly by the constable who was slowly advancing along the pavement in his direction.
